#. type: Content of: <chapter><title>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:6
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introdução"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:8
msgid ""
"With the <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ you can "
"enjoy all benefits of professional services and exclusive Business Features "
"offered by the OTRS Group. Optimize your internal &amp; external "
"communication for more service quality – flexibly adjustable to your "
"operating scenario."
msgstr ""
"Com o  <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ você pode "
"desfrutar  de tos os benefícios dos serviços profissionais empresariais "
"exclusivos e recursos oferecidos pelo grupo OTRS. Otimize seu  internal "
"&amp; comunicação externa para obter mais qualidade de serviço - "
"flexibilidade operacional ajustável ao seu cenário."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:11
msgid ""
"The sleek and fast framework of OTRS 6 is the base for the <ulink url="
"\"https://www.otrs.com/otrs-business-solution-improving-customer-service/"
"\"><emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™</ulink>.  On "
"top are available for you additionally an exclusive set of features. These "
"include the <ulink url=\"https://www.otrs.com/otrs-business-solution-"
"improving-customer-service/#OTRS-Business-Solution-Cloud-Services"
"\">integrated Cloud Services</ulink> of the <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS "
"Business Solution</emphasis>™ that you can flexibly activate or deactivate "
"according to your deployment scenarios."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:17
msgid ""
"Additionally you have the choice between 3, 7 or an unlimited number of "
"various <ulink url=\"https://www.otrs.com/otrs-business-solution-improving-"
"customer-service/#OTRS-Business-Solution-Cloud-Services\">freely selectable "
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ Features</ulink> "
"- depending on you contract level.  Profit also from regular, free updates, "
"the best OTRS security and support as well as installation and configuration "
"carried out by our consultants."
msgstr ""
"Além disso, você escolhe entre 3, 7 ou de diferentes de um número ilimitado "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.otrs.com/otrs-business-solution-improving-customer-"
"service/#OTRS-Business-Solution-Cloud-Services\">selecionado livremente "
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ Característica</"
"ulink> - dependendo do nível do contrato, regular também sem fins lucrativos "
"com atualização gratuita , OTRS o melhor em segurança e apoio, bem como "
"instalação e configuração efetuadas pelos nossos clientes."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><title>
#: en/content/upgrading.xml:6
msgid "Upgrading to <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™"
