#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:52
msgid ""
"Controls whether or not agents should be able to start chats with customers "
"directly."
msgstr ""
"Controla-se ou não os agentes capazes de iniciar o chat diretamente com "
"clientes."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:57
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::ChatDirection::AgentToAgent</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:60
msgid "Controls whether or not agents should be able chat with each other."
msgstr ""
"Controla-se ou não os agentes capazes de iniciar o chat, um com os outros."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:65
msgid ""
"<literal>ChatEngine::PermissionGroup::ChatReceivingAgents</literal>, "
"<literal>ChatEngine::PermissionGroup::ChatNotificationAgents</literal>, "
"<literal>ChatEngine::PermissionGroup::ChatStartingAgents</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:68
msgid ""
"Defines groups for the certain features. Receiving: Groups which can receive "
"and accept chat requests. Notification: Groups which can receive "
"notifications about new/pending chat requests. Starting: Groups which are "
"allowed to start new chats at all."
msgstr ""
"Definir os grupos para determinadas funções. Recebimentos: Os grupos podem "
"receber e aceitar solicitações no chat. Notificações: Os grupos podem "
"receber notificações sobre novas/solicitações de chat pendentes. Iniciando: "
"Os grupos estão autorizados para iniciar novos chats com todos ."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:73
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::DefaultAgentName</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:76
msgid ""
"A default name which should be displayed to customers and public users "
"instead of the real name of the chatting agents. If empty or disabled, the "
"real agent name will be shown."
msgstr ""
"Um nome padrão que deve ser exibido para os clientes e usuários em lugar do "
"nome verdadeiro do agente de chatting. Se estiver vazio ou desativado, o "
"verdadeiro nome do agente será mostrado."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:81
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::DefaultAgentNameNumbers</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:84
msgid ""
"Controls whether or not numbers should be added to the agents default name "
"in case more than one agent is in a chat to allow customers/public users to "
"distinguish between the different agents (e.g. \"Support Agent 1\", "
"\"Support Agent 2\" etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Controla-se os números que não devem ser adicionados aos agentes, nome "
"padrão no caso de mais de um agente que está em um chat para permitir que os "
"clientes/usuários para distinguir entre os diferentes agentes ( por exemplo "
"\" Agente de suporte 1 \", Agente de suporte 2\", etc)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:89
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::PublicInterface::AllowChatChannels</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:92
msgid ""
"Defines, if chat channel selection should be enabled for public users. If "
"set to \"no\", chats from public users will go to the default channel "
"automatically (ChatEngine::DefaultChatChannel)."
msgstr ""
"Define-se canal de chat, uma seleção ativa de usuários. Se definido como "
"\"não\", os usuários do chat vão para o canal padrão automaticamente "
"(ChatEngine::DefaultChatChannel)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:97
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::PublicInterface::AvailabilityCheck</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:100
msgid ""
"Defines, if chat channels should only be selectable in the public interface "
"if at least one agent with <link linkend=\"chat-permissions\">sufficient "
"permissions</link> is available in this channel."
msgstr ""
"Define-se os canais de chat que devem ser selecionáveis pelo menos na "
"interface pública por um agente com<link linkend=\"chat-permissions"
"\">permissões suficientes</link> está disponível neste canal."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:105
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::CustomerInterface::AllowChatChannels</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:108
msgid ""
"Defines, if chat channel selection should be enabled for customer users. If "
"set to \"no\", chats from customer users will go to the default channel "
"automatically (<literal>ChatEngine::DefaultChatChannel</literal>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:113
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::CustomerInterface::AvailabilityCheck</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:116
msgid ""
"Defines, if chat channels should only be selectable in the customer "
"interface if at least one agent with <link linkend=\"chat-permissions"
"\">sufficient permissions</link> is available in this channel."
msgstr ""
"Define-se os canais de chat que devem ser selecionáveis pelo menos na "
"interface do cliente por uma agente <link linkend=\"chat-permissions"
"\">permissão suficiente</link> está disponível neste canal."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:121
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::CustomerThreshold</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:124
msgid ""
"Amount of minutes which need to pass before a <emphasis>no agent is "
"available</emphasis> message is being displayed to the customer/public user "
"who started the chat request. The message can be configured using "
"<literal>ChatEngine::Texts::CustomerFrontend::NoAgentsAvailable::NewTicket</"
"literal> or <literal>ChatEngine::Texts::CustomerFrontend::NoAgentsAvailable::"
"AddToExisiting</literal> (customer interface) and <literal>ChatEngine::"
"Texts::PublicFrontend::NoAgentsAvailable</literal> (public interface)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:129
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::AgentOnlineThreshold</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:132
msgid ""
"If an agent is not active in OTRS within this threshold, they will be "
"automatically set to <emphasis>unavailable for chat</emphasis> (see <link "
"linkend=\"chat-setup-availability\">Agents: Set up availability</link>)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:137
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::DefaultChatChannel</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:140
msgid ""
"Name of the default chat channel. This channel must not be created manually "
"and can't be deleted. This channel is taken as target chat channel in case "
"chat channel selection is disabled for any interface."
msgstr ""
"Nome do canal de chat padrão. Este canal não deve ser criado manualmente e "
"não pode ser excluída. este canal é tomado como alvo no canal de chat, em "
"caso de seleção de canal de chat está desativado para qualquer interface."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:145
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::ChatTTL</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:148
msgid ""
"After how many hours a closed chat should be deleted from the database. "
"Closed chats can still be viewed and downloaded by customers. After a chat "
"has been deleted from the database, it will no longer be possible for "
"customers to view or download it."
msgstr ""
"Depois de muitas horas o chat deve ser fechado e excluído do banco de dados. "
"O chats fechados podem ainda ser visualizados e baixados pelos clientes. "
"Depois que o chat for excluído do banco de dados, deixará de ser possível a "
"visualização ou  download para o cliente. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:153
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::ChatDecayTime</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:156
msgid ""
"After how many days chats which are not closed should be deleted from the "
"database automatically in order to keep the database clean. Please note that "
"this setting can possibly delete chats which are still in use if they are "
"older than the configured amount of days."
msgstr ""
"Depois de muitos dias os chats não fechados, devem ser excluídos do banco de "
"dados automaticamente, a fim de manter o banco de dados limpos. Por favor, "
"note que esta definição pode eventualmente excluir um chat que ainda está em "
"uso, se forem mais antigos, que a quantidade de dias configurado."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:161
msgid "<literal>ChatEngine::ChatOrder</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:164
msgid ""
"Defines, if new chats should be prepended or appended to the list of active "
"chats in the active chats widget in the chat manager."
msgstr ""
"Define-se os novos chats que devem ser anexado ou desanexado a lista ativa "
"dos chats dos chats widget ativos no gerenciador de chat."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:172 en/content/features/video-calls.xml:46
msgid "Setup"
msgstr "Setup"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:174
msgid ""
"In order to be able to create your first chat, you need to setup certain "
"things in your OTRS instance."
msgstr ""
"A fim de ser capaz de criar o seu  primeiro chat, você precisa configurar "
"determinados instrumentos em sua instância no OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:177
msgid "Admin: Create chat channels and assign permissions"
msgstr "Administrar: Criar canais de chat e atribuir permissões"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:179
msgid ""
"In the admin area in OTRS, you'll find a new entry <emphasis>Chat Channel</"
"emphasis> (<literal>AdminChatChannel</literal>). Use this screen to add new "
"channels. You'll need to assign an existing agent group to each channel "
"you'll create. You can use the screens <emphasis>Agents ↔ Groups</emphasis> "
"or <emphasis>Agents ↔ Roles</emphasis> to assign permissions. There are new "
"chat-specific permissions which are described below."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><variablelist><title>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:183
msgid "Available Chat Permissions"
msgstr "Chat com permissões disponíveis"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:185
msgid "<literal>CHAT_OBSERVER</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:188
msgid ""
"Users with this permission type will only be able to observe chats in this "
"channel after they have been invited to them. They will not be able to "
"accept or observe chats in this channel on their own and if they are the "
"only agents currently available in this channel, customers/public users will "
"not be able to create a new chat in this channel. Observers can still invite "
"other agents to a chat they currently observe."
msgstr ""
"Os usuários com este tipo de permissão serão capazes de observar os chats "
"neste canal após serem convidados. Eles não serão capazes de aceitar ou "
"observar os chats neste canal, cliente/usuário não será capaz de criar um "
"novo chat neste canal. Os observadores não podem  convidar ainda outros "
"agentes a um chat e observar atualmente."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:193
msgid "<literal>CHAT_PARTICIPANT</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:196
msgid ""
"Users with this permission type will be able to take part in a chat, but "
"only after they get invited to it. After they're in a chat, they can change "
"the chat channel, discard the chat etc. They will not be able to accept a "
"customer/public user chat request on their own."
msgstr ""
"Os usuários com este tipo de permissão será capaz de tomar parte de um chat, "
"mas só depois de  convidados. Depois estão no chat, eles podem alterar ou "
"descartar  o canal de chat etc.. Eles não serão capazes de aceitar um "
"cliente/usuário do chat na sua própria solicitação."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:201
msgid "<literal>CHAT_OWNER</literal>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:204
msgid ""
"Users with this permission type will be able to accept chat customer/public "
"requests and do all kinds of observer and participant actions on a chat."
msgstr ""
"Os utilizadores com este tipo de permissão serão capazes de aceitar clientes "
"de chat/pedidos do público e fazer todos os tipos de observador e "
"participante de ações de um chat."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:212
msgid ""
"To use the chat in general, agents still need to have at least ro "
"permissions to the groups set up in <literal>ChatEngine::PermissionGroup::"
"ChatReceivingAgents</literal> and <literal>ChatEngine::PermissionGroup::"
"ChatStartingAgents</literal>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:217
msgid "Agents: Select Active Chat Channels"
msgstr "Agentes: selecionar canais de chat ativos"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:220
msgid "Setting up preferred chat channels"
msgstr "Criando canais de chat preferidos"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:222
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/chat/ChatAgentPrefChatChannels.png\" scalefit="
"\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/chat/ChatAgentPrefChatChannels.png\" scalefit="
"\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:227
msgid ""
"As an agent, you'll need to select in which chat channels you want to be "
"available. Customers will only be able to create a new chat request on a "
"certain channel if at least one agent with owner permissions has selected "
"this channel in their preferences and is set as available for external chats "
"(see next section)."
msgstr ""
"Como um agente, você precisará selecionar os canais de chat que você deseja "
"está disponível. Os clientes serão capazes de criar uma solicitação de chat "
"em um determinado canal, ao menos que um agente com permissão do "
"proprietário escolher este canal em sua preferencias, definido como "
"disponível para o chat externo (Visualizar a seção seguinte)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:231
msgid "Agents: Set up Availability"
msgstr "Agentes: configurar a disponibilidade"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:234
msgid "Setting up Chat Availability"
msgstr "Configurando a disponibilidade do chat"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><screenshot>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:236
msgid ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/chat/ChatAgentToggleAvailability.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"
msgstr ""
"<graphic fileref=\"screenshots/chat/ChatAgentToggleAvailability.png\" "
"scalefit=\"1\" width=\"100%\" contentdepth=\"100%\"></graphic>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:241
msgid ""
"To be available for any chats, you'll need to use the chat toolbar switch. "
"It's a three-way switch with these states: unavailable for chats (empty "
"circle), available for internal (agent-to-agent) chats (empty circle with "
"tick sign), available for internal and external (customer-to-agent, public-"
"to-agent) chats (filled circle with tick sign). Just click the toggle in "
"order to change your availability."
msgstr ""
"Estar disponível para qualquer chat, você precisará utilizar um interruptor "
"de uma barra de ferramentas de chat. É um interruptor de três vias com estes "
"estados: indisponível para chat (círculo vazio), disponível para interno "
"(agente para agente) chats (círculo vazio com sinal), disponível para "
"interno e externo (cliente para agente, público para agente) chats(círculo "
"preenchido com sinal). Basta clicar o botão do pedido para alterar sua "
"disponibilidade."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/features/chat.xml:245
msgid ""
"Your availability will be reset to <emphasis>internal chats only</emphasis> "
"each time you log in to OTRS again."
msgstr ""

