"configurado para exibir."

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:6
msgid "The Dynamic Field <emphasis>Database</emphasis>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:9
msgid ""
"This feature implements a dynamic field of the type <emphasis>Database</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:15
msgid ""
"This feature implements a generic dynamic field type, which offers the "
"possibility to gather data from external databases.  Such connected datasets "
"can be searched and filtered using additional masks."
msgstr ""
"Este recurso implementa um tipo de campo dinâmico genérico, que oferece a "
"possibilidade de recolher dados a partir do banco de dados externos. Tais "
"conjuntos de dados conectados pode ser pesquisado e filtrado utilizando "
"máscaras adicionais."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:19
msgid ""
"Related found and marked datasets can be saved to the particular tickets "
"through the dynamic field."
msgstr ""
"encontrado e marcado o conjunto de dados relacionados, podem ser salvas para "
"o ticket particular através do campo dinâmico."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:22
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Database</emphasis> dynamic fields can be created the same way, as "
"the default dynamic fields are created."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:29
msgid ""
"The following list of configuration options can be used for this feature."
msgstr ""
"A seguinte lista de opções de configuração podem ser utilizadas para este "
"recurso."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:32
msgid "Adding a <emphasis>Database</emphasis> Dynamic Field"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:34
msgid ""
"This feature implements a configuration interface to create dynamic fields "
"of the type <emphasis>Database</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:37
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Database</emphasis> dynamic fields can be created the same way, as "
"the default dynamic fields are created. For this switch to the "
"<emphasis>Admin → Ticket Settings → Dynamic Fields</emphasis> view. In this "
"mask you can select the <emphasis>Database</emphasis> field from the ticket "
"drop down box on the left side. Currently it's not possible to use the "
"<emphasis>Database</emphasis> dynamic field in the article context."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:43
msgid "Configuration <emphasis>General - Name</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:46
msgid ""
"Dynamic fields of the type <emphasis>Database</emphasis> need a unique name "
"just like other dynamic fields, too. This name has to contain only "
"alphanumeric values. This name will be used for internal handling of the "
"field but will not be displayed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:51
msgid "Configuration <emphasis>General - Label</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:54
msgid ""
"The label can be individually set and can contain white spaces etc. It will "
"be used as the field label in the different views."
msgstr ""
"A etiqueta pode ser definida individualmente e pode conter espaços em branco "
"etc. Ele será utilizado como etiqueta do campo nas diferentes visualizações."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:59
msgid "Configuration <emphasis>General - Field order</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:62
msgid ""
"The field order allows a administrator to change the order of created "
"dynamic fields. If this configuration get changed the general field order "
"will be adjusted and other dynamic fields will be moved one position back."
msgstr ""
"A ordem do campo permite que um administrador altere a ordem do campo "
"dinâmico criado. Se mudar esta configuração obterá a ordem do campo geral "
"que será ajustada e outros campos dinâmicos serão removidos para uma posição "
"de volta."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:67
msgid "Configuration <emphasis>General - Valid</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:70
msgid ""
"To use the dynamic field in the configured OTRS views it has to be set as "
"valid. If the field is set to <emphasis>invalid</emphasis> it will disappear "
"from all the configured views but no data will be lost."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:77
msgid "Configuration of the External Data Source"
msgstr "Configuração externa da fonte de dados"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:79
msgid ""
"Before an external database can be searched and the results be saved at the "
"ticket through the dynamic field, the credentials have to be stored in the "
"configuration of the dynamic field."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-database.xml:84
msgid "Dynamic Field Database Admin screen"
