"This screen behaves similar to new email and phone screens, with some "
"notable exceptions. Instead of email addresses, <emphasis>Recipients</"
"emphasis> field accepts only phone numbers in international format, complete "
"with plus sign (+)  and country code. You can also search for customer users "
"via this field, provided they have a valid phone number stored in preference "
"field which is configured in cloud service configuration screen."
